#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kgraphviewer; is a &graphviz; &dot; graph viewer. The &graphviz; programs "
"are free-software layout engines for graphs. &kgraphviewer; displays the "
"graphs in a modern, user-friendly &GUI;. It has the following features:"
msgstr ""
"&kgraphviewer; je &graphviz; &dot; pregledovalnik grafov. Programi, ki jih "
"ustvari &graphviz; so prosta programska oprema za razporeditev grafov. "
"&kgraphviewer; prikaže grafe v modernem, uporabniku prijaznem &GUI; "
"(grafičnem vmesniku). Ima naslednje lastnosti:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is a screenshot of &kgraphviewer;"
msgstr "Tu je posnetek zaslona &kgraphviewer;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main &kgraphviewer; window displaying one of the &graphviz; examples"
msgstr "Glavno okno &kgraphviewer;-ja prikazuje enega od primerov &graphviz;-a"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming;"
msgstr "Povečevanje;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading of several graphs in tabs at the same time;"
msgstr "Nalaganje več grafov v zavihkih hkrati;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Storage of a list of recent files;"
msgstr "Shranjevanje seznama nedavnih datotek;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "A bird's eye view of the graph;"
msgstr "Pogled iz ptičje perspektive na graf;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graph panning by mouse dragging;"
msgstr "Premikanje grafa z miško;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full-featured printing;"
msgstr "Tiskanje z vsemi lastnostmi;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Perfect drawing of all &graphviz; example graphs;"
msgstr "Popolno risanje vseh &graphviz;-ovih primerov grafov;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Node and edge colors and all node shapes are supported;"
msgstr "Podprte so vse barve in oblike vozlišč in povezav;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatic choice of &dot; for directed graphs and &neato; for undirected "
"ones;"
msgstr ""
"Samodejna izbira &dot;-a za usmerjene grafe in &neato;-a za neusmerjene;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manual or automatic reloading with user confirmation of (externally) "
"modified files (configurable);"
msgstr ""
"Ročno ali samodejno ponovno nalaganje s potrdilom uporabnika (zunanje) "
"spremenjenih datotek (nastavljivo);"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opening of new program instances as new tabs in an existing instance "
"(configurable);"
msgstr ""
"Na novo odpiranje programa kot novih zavihkov v obstoječem oknu "
"(nastavljivo);"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help system;"
msgstr "Sistem pomoči;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Internationalization."
msgstr "Internacionalizacija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planned features are:"
msgstr "Načrtovane funkcije so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Eventual use of the &qanava; library to support internal graphs "
"representation;"
msgstr ""
"Sčasoma bomo uporabljali knjižnico &qanava;, da podpiramo predstavitev "
"notranjih grafov;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save session data about graphs (layout program used, zoom factor, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"Shraniti podatke seje o grafih (uporabljen program za razpored, faktor "
"povečave &etc;)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Integration in &kate; and &konqueror; (so that a change in &kate;'s view of "
"the graph would re-layout and reload the file in &kgraphviewer;);"
msgstr ""
"Integracija v &kate; in &konqueror; (da bo sprememba v &kate;-ovem pogledu "
"na graf ponovno razporedila in naložila datoteko v &kgraphviewer;);"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Menu to open the file in &kate; <emphasis>or</emphasis> to open a katepart "
"inside the &kgraphviewer; window;"
msgstr ""
"Meni za odpiranje datoteke v programu &kate; <emphasis>ali</emphasis> za "
"odpiranje dela katepart v oknu &kgraphviewer;;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Loading of large and huge graphs (currently, there are performance problems "
"at around 1000 nodes, and a hack to ignore nodes above a specified limit);"
msgstr ""
"Nalaganje velikih grafov (trenutno se pojavijo težave pri približno 1000 "
"vozliščih in obstaja hek, da program prezre vozlišča čez določeno mejo);"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Progressive support of more and more &dot; attributes and values;"
msgstr "Progresivna podpora vedno večih &dot; lastnosti in vrednosti;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Layout in background (with threading in order not to block the interface, "
"with a progress bar)."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev v ozadju (z nitenjem, da ne blokira vmesnika, z vrstico napredka)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that this program includes code from the GPL tool &kcachegrind; by "
"Josef Weidendorfer, with his authorization."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da ta program vsebuje kodo GPL-jevega orodja &kcachegrind; od "
"Josef Weidendorfer, z njegovim pooblastilom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note also that the printing system is from the &calligra;'s &kexi; database "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte tudi, da je sistem za tiskanja od &calligra;-ve &kexi; "
"aplikacije za podatkovne baze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Other required software: &kgraphviewer; is a program that uses the "
"&graphviz; tool &dot; for graph layout. Its dependencies are:"
msgstr ""
"Ostala potrebna programska oprema: &kgraphviewer; je program, ki uporablja "
"orodje &graphviz;-a &dot; za razporeditev grafov. Njegove odvisnosti so:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &Qt; and &kde-frameworks; libraries version 5.x;"
msgstr "Knjižnice &Qt; in &kde-frameworks; verzije 5.x;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &graphviz; tools as externals programs (tested with version 2.8);"
msgstr "&graphviz;-ova orodja kot zunanji programi (testirano z verzijo 2.8);"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &boost; library version 1.36."
msgstr "Knjižnica &boost; verzije 1.36."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kgraphviewer;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kgraphviewer;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno Okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window displays the loaded graphs, each in its own tab. Initially, "
"if you start &kgraphviewer; without arguments, its main window will be empty "
"as in the screenshot below. In this case, the toolbar contains only the "
"<guibutton>Open...</guibutton> and the (empty) <guibutton>Open Recent</"
"guibutton> buttons. Click on the first one to open the standard "
"<guilabel>Open File</guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno prikazuje naložene grafe, vsakega v svojem zavihku. Če zaženete "
"&kgraphviewer; brez argumentov, bo glavno okno prazno, kot je prikazano na "
"spodnjem posnetku zaslona. V tem primeru bo orodna vrstica vsebovala le "
"gumbe <guibutton>Odpri...</guibutton> in (prazen) <guibutton>Odpri nedavno</"
"guibutton>. Kliknite na prvega, da odprete standardno pogovorno okno za "
"<guilabel>Odpiranje Datoteke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The initial main window when opening &kgraphviewer; for the "
"first time</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Začetno glavno okno pri prvem odpiranju &kgraphviewer;-ja</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The initial main window when opening &kgraphviewer; for the first "
"time</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Začetno glavno okno pri prvem odpiranju &kgraphviewer;-ja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>The initial main window when opening &kgraphviewer; for the first "
"time</para>"
msgstr "<para>Začetno glavno okno pri prvem odpiranju &kgraphviewer;-ja</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After selecting one or several &dot; files, the main window looks like the "
"next screenshot below:"
msgstr ""
"Potem ko izberete eno od datotek &dot;, bo glavno okno izgledalo, kot na "
"spodnjem posnetku zaslona:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The main window of &kgraphviewer; with several files opened</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Glavno okno &kgraphviewer;-ja z nekaj odprtimi datotekami</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The main window of &kgraphviewer; with several files opened</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Glavno okno &kgraphviewer;-ja z nekaj odprtimi datotekami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<para>The main window of &kgraphviewer; with several files opened</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavno okno &kgraphviewer;-ja z nekaj odprtimi datotekami</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you can see, if the graph is larger than the available area, a bird's-eye "
"view is shown in one corner. You can choose with the context menu whether "
"the optimal position of this overview should be automatically computed for "
"you, or place it where you want yourself."
msgstr ""
"Kot lahko vidite, če je graf večji od dodeljenega območja, se v enem od "
"kotov prikaže pogled iz ptičje perspektive. S kontekstnim menijem lahko "
"izberete, ali naj se optimalni položaj tega pregleda samodejno izračuna za "
"vas ali pa ga postavite, kamor želite sami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving the Graph inside the Window"
msgstr "Premikanje Grafa v Oknu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "To move the graph, you can:"
msgstr "Graf lahko premaknete tako, da:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click and drag it;"
msgstr "Ga kliknete in povlečete;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the scroll bars;"
msgstr "Uporabite drsne trakove;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press the arrows keys;"
msgstr "Pritisnete na tipke s puščicami;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click somewhere in the bird's-eye view;"
msgstr "Kliknete nekam na pogled iz ptičje perspektive;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the mouse wheel (up and down with no modifier, left and right with the "
"&Alt; key pressed);"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite kolesce miške (gor in dol, če niste spremenili, ter levo in desno, "
"če pritisnete tipko &Alt;);"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "or click and drag in the bird's-eye view."
msgstr "ali kliknete in povlečete v pogledu iz ptičje perspektive."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming"
msgstr "Povečevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To zoom, you can either use the <guibutton><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"kgraphviewer-but-zoomin.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guibutton> and "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"kgraphviewer-but-zoomout.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> </guibutton> toolbar buttons to zoom in and out, or hold "
"down the &Shift; key while rolling your mouse wheel. While zooming in, the "
"red rectangle in the bird's-eye view that indicates the displayed zone gets "
"smaller and smaller. If it were to get smaller than 10 pixels in its shorter "
"side, it will be replaced by a filled red rectangle in order to stay "
"visible. You can see that on the screenshot below."
msgstr ""
"Da povečate, lahko uporabite gumbe iz orodne vrstice "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"kgraphviewer-but-zoomin.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> </guibutton> in <guibutton><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"kgraphviewer-but-zoomout.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guibutton>, da povečate in "
"pomanjšate, ali pa držite tipko &Shift; med vrtenjem kolesca miške. Medtem "
"ko povečujete, se bo rdeči pravokotnik v pogledu iz ptičje perspektive, ki "
"označuje prikazano območje, vedno bolj manjšal. Če se bo zmanjšal na manj "
"kot 10 pikslov na krajši strani, bo namesto njega prikazan poln rdeč "
"pravokotnik, da bo ostal viden. To lahko vidite na posnetku zaslona spodaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A graph at the maximal zoom in level</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Graf pri največji stopnji povečave</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A graph at the maximal zoom in level</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Graf pri največji stopnji povečave</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>A graph at the maximal zoom in level</para>"
msgstr "<para>Graf pri največji stopnji povečave</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Zooming is limited in both directions by a factor of 10. You can see below "
"the maximum zoom-out factor on a graph."
msgstr ""
"Povečevanje je omejeno v obe smeri s faktorjem 10. Spodaj lahko vidite "
"največji faktor pomanjševanja na grafu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A graph at the maximum zoom-out level</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Graf pri največji stopnji pomanjšave</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A graph at the maximum zoom-out level</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Graf pri največji stopnji pomanjšave</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>A graph at the maximum zoom-out level</para>"
msgstr "<para>Graf pri največji stopnji pomanjšave</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graph Files Handling"
msgstr "Obdelava Datotek z Grafi"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files Modified on Disk"
msgstr "Datoteke spremenjene na Disku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a file currently loaded in &kgraphviewer; is modified by another program, "
"the following dialog is shown:"
msgstr ""
"Če je datoteka, ki je trenutno naložena v &kgraphviewer;, spremenjena iz "
"drugega programa, se bo prikazalo naslednje pogovorno okno:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dialog to reload a file modified on disk</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Pogovorno okno za ponovno nalaganje datoteke, ki je bila "
"spremenjena na disku</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dialog to reload a file modified on disk</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Pogovorno okno za ponovno nalaganje datoteke, ki je bila spremenjena "
"na disku</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Dialog to reload a file modified on disk</para>"
msgstr ""
"<para>Pogovorno okno za ponovno nalaganje datoteke, ki je bila spremenjena "
"na disku</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to reload the graph or to ignore the change. You can also get "
"&kgraphviewer; to remember your choice, so it will do the same thing the "
"next time. If you later want to modify your choice, choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"&kgraphviewer;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. See <xref linkend="
"\"kgraphviewer-configuration\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Odločite se lahko, ali boste graf ponovno naložili ali boste ignorirali "
"spremembe. &kgraphviewer; lahko prav tako prilagodite, da si bo zapomnil "
"vašo odločitev in naslednjič naredil isto. Če želite kasneje spremeniti "
"svojo odločitev, izberite element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kgraphviewer;...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> točko menija. Glejte <xref linkend=\"kgraphviewer-configuration"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Files and Windows"
msgstr "Datoteke in Okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you open a graph file from outside a running &kgraphviewer; instance, "
"&eg; from a file browser or the command line, you have the choice to open a "
"new &kgraphviewer; window or to open the graph in a new tab in the existing "
"window. This is done with the dialog below."
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete datoteko z grafom izven &kgraphviewer;-ja, &eg; iz brskalnika "
