#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:463
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous Functions"
msgstr "Razne funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu, usually obtained by clicking the &RMB; in the graph view, "
"offers some other possibilities:"
msgstr ""
"Kontekstni meni, ponavadi pridobljen z desnim klikom v pogledu na graf, "
"ponuja nekaj drugih možnosti:"

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Layout"
msgstr "Razpored"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows to choose between various &graphviz; layout algorithms or to "
"choose your own one. The entries, as described on the &graphviz; homepage, "
"are the following:"
msgstr ""
"To omogoča izbiro med različnimi &graphviz;-ovimi algoritmi za razporejanje, "
"lahko pa izberete svojega. Vnosi, kot je opisano na domači strani &graphviz;-"
"a, so naslednji:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "&dot;"
msgstr "&dot;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&dot; algorithm, default for directed graphs. It produces "
"<quote>hierarchical</quote> or layered drawings of directed graphs. The "
"layout algorithm lays edges in the same direction (top to bottom, or left to "
"right), and then attempts to avoid edge crossings and to reduce edge length."
msgstr ""
"Algoritem &dot;, privzet za usmerjene grafe. Proizvede <quote>hierarhične</"
"quote> ali večplastne risbe usmerjenih grafov. Algoritem za razporejanje "
"razporedi povezave v isto smer (od vrha proti dnu ali od leve proti desni) "
"in se nato poizkuša izogniti prekrižanim povezavam in zmanjšati dolžino "
"povezav."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid "&neato;"
msgstr "&neato;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&neato; algorithm, default for undirected graphs. It produces <quote>spring "
"model</quote> layouts. It uses the Kamada-Kawai algorithm, which is "
"equivalent to statistical multi-dimensional scaling."
msgstr ""
"Algoritem &neato;, privzet za neusmerjene grafe. Proizvede postavitve "
"<quote>vzmetnega modela</quote>. Uporablja algoritem Kamada-Kawai, ki je "
"enakovreden statističnemu večdimenzionalnem skaliranju."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid "&twopi;"
msgstr "&twopi;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&twopi; algorithm, for directed and undirected graphs. Radial layout, after "
"Graham Wills 1997."
msgstr ""
"Algoritem &twopi; za usmerjene in neusmerjene grafe. Radialna postavitev, po "
"Grahamu Willsu 1997."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "&fdp;"
msgstr "&fdp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:489
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&fdp; algorithm, for undirected graphs. It produces <quote>spring model</"
"quote> layouts. It implements the Fruchterman-Reingold heuristic including a "
"multigrid solver that handles larger graphs and clustered undirected graphs."
msgstr ""
"Algoritem &fdp; za neusmerjene grafe. Proizvede postavitve <quote>vzmetnega "
"modela</quote>. Izvaja Fruchterman-Reingoldovo hevristiko, vključno z "
"večmrežnim reševalnikom, ki obravnava večje grafe in gručaste neusmerjene "
"grafe."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "&circo;"
msgstr "&circo;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&circo; algorithm. It produces a circular layout, after Six and Tollis 1999, "
"Kauffman and Wiese 2002. Suitable for certain diagrams of multiple cyclic "
"structures."
msgstr ""
"Algoritem &circo;. Proizvede krožno postavitev, po Six in Tollis 1999, "
"Kaufman in Wiese 2002. Primeren za določene diagrame večih krožnih struktur."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify Layout Command…"
msgstr "Določi ukaz za postavitev…"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog allowing you to specify a layout command executed by the "
"shell. This command should accept one parameter, the graph file name, and "
"write its layout on stdout in the xdot language. This way, you can give "
"specific options to one of the previous commands, or apply a filter "
"modifying your graph before running it through &dot;."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča, da določite ukaz za postavitev, ki ga "
"izvede lupina. Ta ukaz sprejme le en parameter, ime datoteke z grafom, in "
"izpiše svojo razporeditev na standardni izhod v jeziku xdot. Na ta način "
"lahko podate določene možnosti enemu prejšnjih ukazov ali uporabite filter, "
"ki spremeni vaš graf preden ga poženete skozi &dot;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset Layout Command to Default"
msgstr "Ponastavi ukaz za postavitev na privzetega"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determine the graph type (directed or not) and apply the default algorithm "
"to it, currently &dot; and &neato; respectively."
msgstr ""
"Določite vrsto grafa (usmerjeni ali neusmerjeni) in uporabite na njem "
"privzeti algoritem, ki je trenutno &dot; ali &neato;."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export Graph"
msgstr "Izvozi Graf"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "As Image…"
msgstr "Kot Sliko…"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows to export the full graph to all supported image formats."
msgstr "Omogoča izvoz celotnega grafa v vse podprte slikovne formate."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable Bird's-Eye View"
